17/12/2010
PRISTINA, Kosovo -- EULEX personnel searched the premises of the ministry of economy and finance, the customs service and three private residences Thursday (December 16th) for information about deals in 2008 involving tobacco imports. Local media reported that the officials under investigation for abuse of office are the chief of Customs Naim Huruglica, and the head of the legal department at the finance ministry, Lulzim Rakuna. (Koha Ditore, Zeri, Lajm, Kosova Sot - 17/12/10)
